{title: I Need Your Mercy }
{subtitle: Clint Brown}
{key: Bb}
{keywords: Mod. Apo. Slow}



[Lead in notes:]  [Db][Eb][F][Db][Ab][Gb][F][Bb7]

[Eb/F]I need Your [Bb2]mercy, I need Your [Gm7]grace
I need Your [Eb2]hand leading the [F2]way
I can't make it with[Bb2]out You not for one [G7]day
I need Your [Cm7]mercy, [Eb/F] I need Your [Bb]grace.


Surely goodness and mercy will follow me all my life
I know I can make it with you by my side 






